oo.gl/eVUsQ2PosZKaRyRX9">就在这里</a>。设置时，我将从我的Twitter帐户中鸣叫一个确切的位置。哦，请带上自己的零食和饮料！无论如何，樱桃今年晚些时候，但希望他们能在周六出门。</p><p>无论如何，本周我有几集Econ 102。我和埃里克（Erik）尝试了一种有趣的新格式，他向我询问了有关各个国家的经济体，我给他快速回答了他们当前的状况。到目前为止，我们已经完成了其中的两个，我们将再做一次： </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8a5d3c8fd0d8d85fcfe87099a0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Analyzing Economies: USA, China, Japan, Russia, India, Korea, and more&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/6yOpnCv0MPCcZbKybk0Ket&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/6yOpnCv0MPCcZbKybk0Ket" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8a97552a3ea8fb4f62aff6af5f&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Analyzing Economies: England, France, Germany, Poland, Turkey, and the EU/European Immigration&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/52nuQvRmuTT7S6ilJoXDYr&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/52nuQvRmuTT7S6ilJoXDYr" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>到本周有趣的事情清单！</p><h4> 1.我们应该从弗朗西斯·斯科特（Francis Scott）钥匙桥崩溃中学到什么？</h4><p>该国最近惊恐地看着一艘货船坠入巴尔的摩的弗朗西斯·斯科特·钥匙桥的支撑支柱之一，<a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collapse_of_the_Francis_Scott_Key_Bridge">倒塌了桥的中间</a>，并造成了六次死亡： </p><div id="youtube2-JIJ-367nd2E" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;JIJ-367nd2E&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" da