rget="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg" width="530" height="795" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:795,&quot;width&quot;:530,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:193185,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9981d368-b4a9-4d1a-accc-fcdede71f9d4_530x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="https://unsplash.com/@chrisyangchrisfilm?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">克里斯·杨（Chris Yang）</a>的<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/man-walking-between-stores-during-night-time-LA57RXF1mSI?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">照片</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>对于这些情况中的每一个，故事都是相同的。由于<em>商业密度</em>较高，该空间蓬勃发展 - 各种各样的企业都挤进了一个小区域。正如我在<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-japanese-cities-are-such-nice">上一篇文章</a>中所写的那样，商业密度的讨论不足。它允许<em>多样化</em>- 在日本，当您外出吃饭时，有一百万餐厅可供选择，它们彼此近。当您去衣服购物时，有一百万个小精品店可以尝试，它们彼此近。这大大增强了购物体验。</p><p>但这不仅仅是多样性；这是<em>独特的</em>。如果您进入Zakkyo建筑物，而一切都只是一个橄榄花园，星巴克或24小时的健身，那么一段时间后，它会很无聊。日本城市的浪漫是，总是有很多全新的发现场所，因此总是值得走来走去并发现东西。</p><p>除非有很多人想创办小型企业，否则这是不可能发生的。<em>东京</em>出现的每个商业空间 - 横田，Zakkyo，底线街机 - 取决于一群想要在那里定位的小型企业。如果不存在这种需求，则空间要么没有填充，要么被链条填充。而且，如果没有小型企业协会团结起来并抵制重建压力，那么日本最具标志性的城市空间最终将变成无聊的企业购物中心 - 并不是因为资本主义的邪恶邪恶不足，而是因为没有小型企业，与之无关。<em>除了</em>在那里放一个无聊的公司购物中心，该空间。</p><p><em>新兴的东京</em>从未深入研究的是<em>为什么</em>日本以如此小的企业为中心。它的一部分是由政策驱动的 - 日本制定了许多政府政策，以支持大型零售业务。其中之一是<a href="https://spinup-000d1a-wp-offload-media.s3.amazonaws.com/faculty/wp-content/uploads/sites/53/2019/06/WhySmallShops.Mak.SS.1998.pdf">大型商店法律</a>，它阻止了密集的城市地区的大型商店。但还有很多其他的。专门针对小型零售业务的广泛而多样化的补贴和支持 - 创业成本援助，翻新援助，低息贷款，税收优惠，对小型企业企业家的培训，社区保护法等。当美国人发现在日本开设一家小型零售业务有多容易时，他们常常感到惊讶： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg" width="606" height="519.1422271223814" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:777,&quot;width&quot;:907,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:606,&quot;bytes&quot;:193946,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F884586be-a633-418a-a535-826c54f84c36_907x777.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>除了使城市环境令人愉悦和令人兴奋之外，在我看来，小型企业主为日本城市主义的许多基本要素提供了关键的选区。</p><p>例如，采取公共安全。当连锁店<a href="https://www.foxbusiness.com/retail/cvs-store-close-dc-thieves-ransack-location-months-leaving-shelves-bare">被掠夺</a>时，公司不会关闭。它的大型商店网络可以吸收损失。但是，当一家小型独立商店被掠夺时，对于所有者来说，这通常是毁灭性的。因此，小型商人对促进公共安全的政策有兴趣，这是日本优秀城市的关键要素之一。</p><p>另一个例子是步行性。连锁店具有名称识别和营销预算；城市地区的小型独立餐厅和商店更多地取决于偶然的人流。因此，拥有出色的火车，可步行的空间和住宅密度是为了吸引更多客户，符合小型商人的利益。当人们问为什么日本拥有世界上最好的火车系统时，很少提到小企业的政治力量，但这似乎是值得探索的因素。</p><p>小型企业为资本主义本身创造了最终的选区。中央计划的经济体很少有一种自发的，充满活力的商业空间，在<em>东京新兴的东京</em>如此充满爱意。小型企业将大量中产阶级变成了资本家，使他们在私有企业所有权制度中有直接的利益。他们强烈倾向于<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/on-small-business/wp/2016/10/12/study-republicans-are-24-percent-more-likely-than-democrats-to-be-business-owners/">投票支持亲企业</a>。</p><p>在美国，自20世纪中叶以来，小型“妈妈”零售业务<a href="https://www.nber.org/books-and-chapters/producer-dynamics-new-evidence-micro-data/role-retail-chains-national-regional-and-industry-results">一直在消失</a>，因为大型连锁店利用其<a href="https://www2.census.gov/ces/wp/2015/CES-WP-15-10.pdf">更高的生产力</a>将其定价。日本顽固地与这种趋势作斗争，这是一件事，它使其城市变得更加充满活力，并且比美国更加持久商业品种。在效率方面，费用是一种成本，但是便宜的东西并不是这个世界上唯一的愉快的东西。</p><p>如果愿意，美国大城市可以改变这一点。 <a href="https://www.retaildive.com/news/banning-sameness-how-retailers-can-work-with-cities-chain-store-restric/388183/">已经有一种动作</a>来限制城市中心的连锁店，但需要与鼓励，培训和支持小型独立零售业务的措施配对。分区改革必须成为其中的一部分，诸如允许要求和限制酒类许可证和电气标志的法规。当然，如果要工作，则需要改进步行性，过境和公共安全。如果城市能够让自己做所有这些事情，我认为他们可以创造出日本城市经验的复制品，那么至少在那个方向上比现在的某些方向要多得多。</p><p>实际上，由于缺乏想要接管家族企业的年轻人，小企业现在<a href="https://www.economist.com/asia/2021/12/04/japans-small-businesses-are-in-trouble">在日本受到威胁</a>。这是平淡的公司购物中心现在比两三十年前更大的日本购物体验的重要原因。但是，正如<em>东京新兴的新</em>零售业务所指出的那样，仍然有很多年轻的日本人想创办<em>新的</em>小型零售业务，因此希望这足以维持世界其他地区已经认识和爱的日本城市主义。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/secrets-of-japanese-urbanism-part?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/secrets-of-japanese-urbanism-part?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p></p>;
